You don't need to come tomorrow.

00:29:16.180 --> 00:29:17.460
I promised you both a four-day holiday.

00:29:17.620 --> 00:29:17.980
Have you forgotten?

00:29:18.900 --> 00:29:21.460
But we haven't finished...

00:29:21.460 --> 00:29:21.940
Yes.

00:29:22.060 --> 00:29:23.420
You've already handled things very well.

