Our wines come from the same region.

00:30:54.540 --> 00:30:55.020
Though

00:30:56.460 --> 00:30:57.820
the brewing techniques differ slightly,

00:30:58.100 --> 00:31:00.940
your wine,
in terms of taste and quality,

00:31:01.300 --> 00:31:03.660
is absolutely good enough
to be marketed internationally

00:31:03.660 --> 00:31:04.620
as high-quality national wines.

00:31:06.500 --> 00:31:07.820
I'm just very surprised.

00:31:08.620 --> 00:31:10.420
