Right now

00:31:16.340 --> 00:31:18.300
is the peak season
for all manufacturers to make wine.

00:31:18.860 --> 00:31:21.260
By the time I find the grapes
and finish brewing,

00:31:21.260 --> 00:31:22.420
the delivery time would long be overdue.

00:31:24.300 --> 00:31:24.780
Besides,

00:31:25.700 --> 00:31:27.940
I don't see it
as giving you the opportunity.

